{"word":"ἐμπίμπρημι","slug":"ἐμπίμπρημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπίμπρημι</b></el> <el>(not <el>ἐμπίμπρημι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>ἐμπιπρᾶν</el> as if from <el>e)mpipra/w</el>\n<el>(<a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>ἐμπιπρᾶν</el>) (<a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <el>ἐνεπίμπρων</el>) (3rd <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>-πίμπρασαν</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ἐμπρήσω</el>) (aor1 <el>ἐνέπρησα</el>) (<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ἐμπεπρήσομαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ἐμπρήσομαι</el> in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> form\n<el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ἐμπρήσομαι</el>) (aor1 <el>ἐνεπρήσθην</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>ἐμπέπρησμαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><i>to kindle, burn, set on fire</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>πυρὸς νῆας ἐνιπρῆσαι</el> <i>to burn them</i> by force of fire, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be on fire</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}